song_lyrics: Shyāmnī chhabī re sakhī, Shyāmnī chhabī,
Jone fulaḍethī chhāī, sakhī Shyāmnī chhabī. ṭek꠶
Fulonā torānī fore, bhamar kare gunjār,
Ango-ang Harine ope, fulaḍānā shaṇagār. Shyām꠶ 1
Fulataṇā gajarā fāve chhe, sundar māhī sugandh. Shyām꠶ 2
Fulataṇo shīr mugaṭ joīne, magan fīre vraj-nār,
Fulataṇī shobhā par jāye, Brahmānand balihār. Shyām꠶ 3
title: Shyāmnī chhabī re sakhī Shyāmnī chhabī
